Phase 8 (NotificationService + Nudges — unified `NotificationService` routing class with `resolvePlatform` (Slack→Teams→email fallback), `EmailNotifier` + Resend, React Email templates (Assignment, Nudge, WeeklyDigest, TrialExpiry), Inngest cron `sendNudges` every 6h with 48h stall + 72h suppression, `weeklyDigest` Monday 9am, wired into assignment creation + completions flow).

